</paragraph>
</caption>
<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="341" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,1605,1975]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,345,1605,1628]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">Distribution.</emphasis>
The 
<typeStatus box="[408,454,1605,1628]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">type</typeStatus>
specimens of the new species were collected at Rawalakot (Azad Jammu and Kashmir province, 
<collectingCountry box="[257,352,1640,1663]" name="Pakistan" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">Pakistan</collectingCountry>
); approximately 
<quantity box="[530,610,1640,1663]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.68" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" unit="m" value="1680.0">1680 m</quantity>
a.s.l., 
<geoCoordinate box="[679,786,1640,1663]" direction="north" orientation="latitude" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" precision="925" value="35.85">
<number box="[679,707,1640,1663]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" value="35.0">35</number>
° 
<number box="[722,753,1640,1663]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" value="51.0">51</number>
’ N
</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate box="[796,897,1640,1663]" direction="east" orientation="longitude" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" precision="925" value="71.8">
<number box="[796,824,1640,1663]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" value="71.0">71</number>
° 
<number box="[840,871,1640,1663]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" value="48.0">48</number>
’ E
</geoCoordinate>
(from Gladstonefamily.net, 
<number box="[1199,1257,1640,1663]" pageId="9" pageNumber="341" value="2015.0">2015</number>
c). No conjecture over its geographic distribution can be made, beyond its presence in the mountains of 
<collectingCountry box="[1063,1153,1675,1698]" name="Pakistan" pageId="9" pageNumber="341">Pakistan</collectingCountry>
and perhaps neighbouring countries.
</paragraph>
